n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><strong>西方國家最撚鐘意打納粹</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:52:56.000Z","msg":"同而家既支國有分別咩 極左極右都有 同法西斯相近啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d308890aaa848204902f85e95f9d4a5dbe52f0e8","tid":2140922,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:55:43.000Z","msg":"Chinazi"},{"pid":"87bb3f1f7b97be09a7790b95fdb695446f32abab","tid":2140922,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:00:50.000Z","msg":"今年係納綷一百年黨慶，有咩想同元首講"},{"pid":"d777aa5e85e6c35f24c5fd8d30da8f54b5cb8b82","tid":2140922,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0f385be3697ee1fc8d13b943c340d91489c656e","tid":2140922,"uid":85751,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:28:39.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">Xilter</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:02:08.000Z","msg":"所羅門日日都提<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcb720dbc8ca62ccde3fe0ae5ee8adc030ec6ad","tid":2140922,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17d588fbd057e7ab6e5a0e249cf048a34554e348","tid":2140922,"uid":319113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b31667f77e86ecdc74e5e45c7f392f7e5736594","tid":2140922,"uid":35348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:22:35.000Z","msg":"孔誥烽 知我所想宣我昐望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:19:41.000Z","msg":"無待了 喊六四情花太惡毒"},{"pid":"4d1937bffe8ab89d005664aa39ce259c7c72040d","tid":2140922,"uid":307398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrK9v3X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrK9v3X.jpg&h=4e93468c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52eaaf49ea4010e215927f251c351ebe86d58598","tid":2140922,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ee209663d19569c9ed9669bd081d86014b1e28","tid":2140922,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"第4帝國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15aa7c0dd04641294c81087c935fc5c9c32a097","tid":2140922,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T14:51:11.000Z","msg":"納粹是以雅利安人優秀的種族主義為立國根據，這個中共是沒有的<br />\n<br />\n盲﹖"}]}